description.purpose:
In this test four accounts are used, each subscribing to all events from the Relevancy contract. The accounts are;
Account4 - own wallet Account1 - own wallet Account2 - own wallet Account3 - own wallet
The event NonIndexedAddressAndNumber(address addr1, uint256 value) is used with the address from account4 in the event fields. The test ensures that all accounts see the event as it is a non indexed address field.
